{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882366692,"sessionID":"ses_2852af65bffej6j1KWUCMrG2mO","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad66b6d001yq9Odk15HVFz0t","messageID":"msg_d7ad66287001AecwhLj8MOIKp7","sessionID":"ses_2852af65bffej6j1KWUCMrG2mO","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_221bec4780bc4846aa6052e2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n2: \n3: ## Summary\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 项目的 router、store、picod 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，提高代码质量和可维护性。\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: ### Background\n12: \n13: router、store 和 picod 模块是 AgentCube 的核心组件：\n14: - **router**: 负责请求路由、负载均衡和流量管理\n15: - **store**: 负责状态存储、数据持久化和缓存管理\n16: - **picod**: 负责轻量级运行时环境管理和资源调度\n17: \n18: 当前这些模块的测试覆盖不足，需要补充单元测试以确保代码质量。\n19: \n20: ### Goal\n21: \n22: 1. 为 router、store、picod 模块编写全面的单元测试\n23: 2. 提高测试覆盖率到目标水平\n24: 3. 确保关键业务逻辑的测试覆盖\n25: 4. 建立持续测试的基础设施\n26: \n27: ### Value\n28: \n29: - 提高代码质量，减少 regression\n30: - 为重构提供安全网\n31: - 提高开发者信心\n32: - 满足质量门禁要求\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## Scope\n37: \n38: ### In-Scope\n39: \n40: - pkg/router 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n41: - pkg/store 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n42: - pkg/picod 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n43: - 关键路径的单元测试\n44: - 边界条件和错误处理测试\n45: - 使用 fake client 或 mock 进行隔离测试\n46: \n47: ### Out-of-Scope\n48: \n49: - 集成测试\n50: - 性能测试\n51: - E2E 测试\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## Acceptance Criteria\n56: \n57: 1. 单元测试通过率 100%\n58: 2. 测试覆盖率目标 ≥ 70%\n59: 3. 所有关键业务逻辑都有对应的测试用例\n60: 4. 测试代码符合 Go 最佳实践\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## Detailed Scope Analysis\n65: \n66: ### 1. router 模块\n67: \n68: 待分析...\n69: \n70: ### 2. store 模块\n71: \n72: 待分析...\n73: \n74: ### 3. picod 模块\n75: \n76: 待分析...\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ## Impact Analysis\n81: \n82: ### Benefits\n83: \n84: 1. **Increased Reliability**: Comprehensive test coverage reduces regression risk\n85: 2. **Safe Refactoring**: Router, store, and picod operations can be safely modified\n86: 3. **Documentation**: Tests serve as executable documentation\n87: 4. **CI Confidence**: Full test suite enables confident continuous integration\n88: \n89: ### Risks\n90: \n91: 1. **Module Complexity**: Each module has different dependencies and interfaces\n92: 2. **State Management**: Store module testing requires careful state isolation\n93: 3. **External Dependencies**: Some components may require HTTP/gRPC mocking\n94: \n95: ### Estimated Test Files\n96: \n97: - `router/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n98: - `store/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n99: - `picod/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n100: \n101: ---\n102: \n103: ## Implementation Plan\n104: \n105: 1. **Phase 1**: Analyze existing code and identify testing gaps\n106: 2. **Phase 2**: Implement router module tests\n107: 3. **Phase 3**: Implement store module tests\n108: 4. **Phase 4**: Implement picod module tests\n109: 5. **Phase 5**: Coverage verification and improvements\n\n(End of file - total 109 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n## Summary\n\n为 AgentCube 项目的 router、store、picod 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，提高代码质量和可维护性。\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nrouter、store 和 picod 模块是 AgentCube 的核心组件：\n- **router**: 负责请求路由、负载均衡和流量管理\n- **store**: 负责状态存储、数据持久化和缓存管理\n- **picod**: 负责轻量级运行时环境管理和资源调度\n\n当前这些模块的测试覆盖不足，需要补充单元测试以确保代码质量。\n\n### Goal","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882366682,"end":1775882366689}}}}
