{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882381881,"sessionID":"ses_2852af65bffej6j1KWUCMrG2mO","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad67d1c001ub442S02Xf1yVA","messageID":"msg_d7ad66f15001qZObRB8hkY7V7z","sessionID":"ses_2852af65bffej6j1KWUCMrG2mO","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_c641f5ceff6d44e7882bc1d9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md","newString":"## Detailed Scope Analysis\n\n### 1. router 模块\n\n**文件结构:**\n- `server.go` (231 lines) - HTTP 服务器主逻辑\n- `backend.go` - 后端池管理\n- `proxy.go` - 代理转发\n- `route.go` - 路由匹配\n- `ratelimit.go` - 限流逻辑\n- `auth.go` - 认证\n- `jwt.go`, `jwt_handler.go`, `jwt_middleware.go` - JWT 处理\n- `session.go`, `session_middleware.go` - 会话管理\n- `logging.go` - 日志\n- `health.go` - 健康检查\n- `config.go` - 配置\n\n**现有测试:**\n- `server_test.go` (167 lines) - 基础初始化测试\n\n**待测试组件:**\n| 组件 | 优先级 | 预估新增行数 |\n|------|--------|-------------|\n| backend.go | 高 | 150 |\n| proxy.go | 高 | 120 |\n| route.go | 高 | 100 |\n| ratelimit.go | 中 | 80 |\n| auth.go | 中 | 60 |\n| jwt*.go | 中 | 100 |\n| session*.go | 中 | 100 |\n| logging.go | 低 | 40 |\n| health.go | 低 | 30 |\n\n**覆盖率目标:** ≥80%\n\n### 2. store 模块\n\n**文件结构:**\n- `store.go` (20 lines) - Store 接口定义\n- `store_valkey.go` (349 lines) - Valkey 实现\n- `store_redis.go` - Redis 实现\n- `errors.go` - 错误类型\n- `singleton.go` - 单例模式\n\n**现有测试:** 无\n\n**测试策略:**\n- 使用 mock 或 interface 隔离测试\n- 不依赖外部 Valkey/Redis 服务\n- 测试所有 Store 接口方法\n\n**待测试方法:**\n| 方法 | 优先级 |\n|------|--------|\n| Ping | 高 |\n| GetSandboxBySessionID | 高 |\n| StoreSandbox | 高 |\n| UpdateSandbox | 高 |\n| DeleteSandboxBySessionID | 高 |\n| ListExpiredSandboxes | 中 |\n| ListInactiveSandboxes | 中 |\n| UpdateSessionLastActivity | 中 |\n\n**覆盖率目标:** ≥90%\n\n### 3. picod 模块\n\n**文件结构:**\n- `server.go` (204 lines) - 主服务器\n- `execute.go` - 命令执行\n- `files.go` - 文件操作\n- `auth.go` - 认证管理\n- `config.go` - 配置\n- `auth_middleware.go` - 认证中间件\n- `health.go` - 健康检查\n\n**现有测试:**\n- `picod_test.go` (833 lines) - 较完整\n- `auth_config_test.go`\n\n**待补充测试:**\n- `execute.go` 错误路径\n- `files.go` 边界情况\n- `auth.go` 边缘情况\n- 更多 auth middleware 场景\n\n**覆盖率目标:** ≥85%","oldString":"## Detailed Scope Analysis\n\n### 1. router 模块\n\n待分析...\n\n### 2. store 模块\n\n待分析...\n\n### 3. picod 模块\n\n待分析..."},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/server.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/session_middleware.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":179,"character":62},"end":{"line":179,"character":77}},"severity":3,"code":"unusedparams","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/gopls/internal/analysis/unusedparams#unusedparams"},"source":"unusedparams","message":"unused parameter: r"}],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/config_test.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":51,"character":13},"end":{"line":51,"character":13}},"severity":3,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/unusedwrite"},"source":"unusedwrite","message":"unused write to field IdleTimeout"},{"range":{"start":{"line":52,"character":21},"end":{"line":52,"character":21}},"severity":3,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/unusedwrite"},"source":"unusedwrite","message":"unused write to field HealthCheckInterval"},{"range":{"start":{"line":53,"character":20},"end":{"line":53,"character":20}},"severity":3,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/unusedwrite"},"source":"unusedwrite","message":"unused write to field HealthCheckTimeout"},{"range":{"start":{"line":54,"character":20},"end":{"line":54,"characte