{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882395995,"sessionID":"ses_2852af65bffej6j1KWUCMrG2mO","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad6c26e001VmQ2NSgRtgLrL1","messageID":"msg_d7ad6b7de001mXdo7ocUvf3RA6","sessionID":"ses_2852af65bffej6j1KWUCMrG2mO","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_df4216270ceb409ab9379797","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md","newString":"## Implementation Plan\n\n1. **Phase 1**: Analyze existing code and identify testing gaps\n2. **Phase 2**: Implement router module tests\n3. **Phase 3**: Implement store module tests  \n4. **Phase 4**: Implement picod module tests\n5. **Phase 5**: Coverage verification and improvements\n\n---\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### 1. 仅集成测试\n\n**方案:** 不写单元测试，只做集成测试。\n\n**被拒绝原因:**\n- 集成测试需要外部服务（Valkey/Redis）运行\n- 测试执行速度慢，不适合 TDD\n- 无法精确定位问题所在模块\n- CI 环境搭建复杂\n\n### 2. 使用第三方测试框架 (ginkgo, testify)\n\n**方案:** 使用 ginkgo 或 testify 框架。\n\n**决策:** 继续使用标准 `testing` 包 + `testify/assert`（与现有项目风格一致）\n\n**被拒绝原因:**\n- 现有代码使用标准 `testing` 包\n- 避免引入额外依赖\n- 保持项目测试风格统一\n\n### 3. 使用真实 Valkey/Redis 服务进行测试\n\n**方案:** 在测试中使用 testcontainer 启动真实数据库服务。\n\n**被拒绝原因:**\n- 测试执行速度慢\n- CI 环境配置复杂\n- 并发测试困难\n- 推荐使用 mock/interface 方案\n\n### 4. Property-Based Testing\n\n**方案:** 使用 `testing/quick` 或 `gopter` 进行属性测试。\n\n**决策:** 后续迭代考虑，当前聚焦传统单元测试\n\n**被拒绝原因:**\n- 需要更多时间投入\n- 传统单元测试优先级更高\n- 可在未来迭代中加入","oldString":"## Implementation Plan\n\n1. **Phase 1**: Analyze existing code and identify testing gaps\n2. **Phase 2**: Implement router module tests\n3. **Phase 3**: Implement store module tests\n4. **Phase 4**: Implement picod module tests\n5. **Phase 5**: Coverage verification and improvements"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/server.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_